key_algorithm.description: The algorithm to use when creating a version

key_iam.description: A map containing the IAM member (key) and role (value) for the key

key_labels.description: A map containing the labels for the key

key_name.description: An arbitrary string name for the key

key_protection_level.description: The protection level to use when creating a version based on this template. Possible values include SOFTWARE, HSM, EXTERNAL, EXTERNAL_VPC. Defaults to SOFTWARE.

key_ring_link.description: The self link for the key ring

rotation_period.description: The rotation period for the key

location.description: Location where the key ring is stored

env.description: The name of the environment (ex: n)

key_ring_iam.description: A map containing the IAM member (key) and role (value) for the key_ring

key_ring_location.description: The location of the key ring

project.description: The project id that will contain the KMS resources

purpose.description: The purpose of the key ring

tnt_code.description: The name of the tenant (ex: adp)
